  <brief_title>Minimum Effective Volume of Lidocaine Costoclavicular Brachial Plexus Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>Minimum Effective Volume of Lidocaine for Ultrasound-Guided Costoclavicular Infraclavicular Brachial Plexus Block</official_title>
